hadiths[283]{hadithnumber,text}:
281,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pakizgi nisf eman hai, Alhamdulillah meezaan ko bhar deta hai, Subhanallah aur Alhamdulillah dono ya ( un mein se her kalma ( zamin w aasman ke beech ko bhar deta hai, Namaz Noor hai, sadqa burhaan hai, sabr ziyaa hai aur Quran terey haq mein ya terey khilaf daleel hoga. her aadmi subh ke waqt apney nafs ka soda karta hai, pas wo usey azad kara leta hai ya halak kar deta hai.'' ( rawahu Muslim w Darmi (1 / 167 padhi. 659 ( w Nasai fil-kubra : 9996 ( . aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ( la Ilaah illallahu Allahu-akbar) zamin w aasman ke beech her chiz ko bhar detey hain.'' maine ye riwayat saheehain mein pai hai na Humaidi ki kitab mein aur na hi al-jaame mein. lekin Darmi ne isey Subhanallah walhamdulillah ke badley zikr kya hai."
282,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisa amal bataaun jiskey zariey Allah khataeyn maaf kar deta hai aur darjaat buland karta hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kya : kyon nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! zarur bataeyn . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nagawari ke bawajud mukammal taur par wuzu karna , masaajid ki taraf ziyada qadam chal kar jana aur Namaz ke baad dusri Namaz ka intizar karna , yehi sarhadi chhawni ki hifazat hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
283,Hazrat Malik bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein : ( فذالکم الرباط (ke alfaz do martaba hain. Muslim aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein teen martaba . rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi (52) .
284,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu karey aur khub achi tarah wuzu karey to uski khataeyn uskey jism se nikal jati hain, yahan tak ke uskey naakhunon ke nichey se bhi nikal jati hain.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim ."
285,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman ya momin banda wuzu karta hai aur wo apna chehra dhota hai to aakhon ke dekhney se honey wali tamam khataeyn pani ke sath ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey ke sath uskey chehrey se nikal jati hain, pas jab wo apney haath dhota hai, to uskey haathon se jo khataeyn sarzad hoti hain, wo pani ke sath ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey ke sath uskey haathon se nikal jati hain, pas jab wo apney paaon dhota hai to uskey paaon se jo khataeyn sarzad hoti hain pani ke sath ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey ke sath uskey paaon se nikal jati hain, yahan tak ke wo gunahon se saaf ho jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
286,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman farz Namaz ka waqt honey par uskey liye achi tarah wuzu karta hai aur uskey khushu w rukoo ka achi tarah ehtimam karta hai to wo us ( Namaz ( se pehley kiye huey gunahon ka kaffara bin jati hai b-sharte-ke kabeera gunahon ka irtikab na ho, aur ye ( farz Namaz se sagheera gunahon ka maaf ho jana ( hamesha ke liye hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
287,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney wuzu kya to teen martaba apney haathon par pani dala , phir kulli ki aur naak jhaadi , phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya , phir teen martaba kohni samet apna daayan haath dhoya , phir teen martaba kohni samet apna baayan haath dhoya , phir apney sar ka masah kya, phir teen martaba apna daayan paaon dhoya , phir teen martaba baayan , phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah ko dekha, aapney merey us wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya, phir farmaya : ''jo shakhs merey us wuzu ki tarah wuzu karta hai, phir do rakatein padhta hai aur wo us doran apney dil mein kisi qism ka khayal na laye to uskey sabiqa gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.'' Bukhari , Muslim , hadees ke alfaz Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1934 w Muslim ."
288,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman wuzu karta hai aur wo apna wuzu achi tarah karta hai phir khada ho kar mukammal tawajjoh ke sath do rakatein padhta hai to uskey liye jannat wajib ho jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
289,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs wuzu karta hai aur achi tarah mukammal wuzu karta hai. phir kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, to uskey liye jannat ke aathon darwazey khol diye jatey hain, wo jis se chahey dakhil ho jaey.'' ( rawahu Muslim w ibnul-aseer fi Jaame al-usool (9/ 336 padhi. 7017 ( Tirmizi ( 55 ( sunan Tirmizi (1 / ۷۹ . ۸۲ ( . Imam Muslim ne usey is tarah apni sahih mein riwayat kya hai. Humaidi ne '' afrad Muslim ''main aur isi tarah ibne-aseer ne '' Jaame al-usool ''main riwayat kya hai. الشیخ محی الدین النووی ne Muslim ki hadees ke aakhir mein zikr kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne ye alfaz zayed naqal kiye hain : ''aey Allah ! mujhey tauba karney walon aur paak rehney walon mein se bana dey .'' wo hadees jisey muhiussunna w sihaah'' main riwayat kya hai, jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achi tarah wuzu karey.'' aakhir tak, Imam Tirmizi ne isey bilkul isi tarah apni Jaame mein riwayat kya hai, lekin) (an Muhammad) se pehley (ash'had) ka zikr nahin."
290,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak meri ummat ke logon ko qiyamat ke din bulaya jaeyga, to wuzu ke nishaanaat ki wajeh se unke haath paaon aur peshani chamakti hogi, pas tum mein se jo shakhs apni chamak ko badhaana chahey to wo badha ley.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 136 w Muslim ."
291,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ka zewar wahan tak hoga jahan tak uskey wuzu ka pani pahunchta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
292,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''durust raho, aur tum uski taqat nahin rakhtay, aur jaan lo ke Namaz tumhara behtareen amal hai, aur wuzu ki hifazat sirf momin shakhs hi kar sakta hai.'' rawahu Malik ( fil-Mauta 1 / 34, 65) w Ahmed ( 5 / 270 padhi. 22778 ( w ibne-Maja ( 277 ( w Darmi (1 / 149 padhi. 661 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 130 padhi. 449 ( ."
293,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu honey ke bawajud wuzu karey to uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi 59) w Abu-Dawood ( 62 ( ."
294,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat ki chaabi Namaz hai aur Namaz ki chaabi tahaarat ( wuzu ( hai.'' , ( 3 / 340 padhi. 14717 ( w Tirmizi (4 ( ."
295,"Hazrat shabeeb bin abi rooh (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr ada ki to Sura Rome ki tilawat farmaai , aap bhool gaey, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to farmaya : '' logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke wo hamarey sath Namaz padhtey hain lekin wo achi tarah wuzu nahin kartey , yehi log to hamen Quran bhala detey hain.'' (sahih ( rawahu Nasai ( 2 / 156 padhi. 948 ( w Ahmed ( 3 / 471 padhi. 15968 ( ."
296,"Hazrat banu-Sulaim ke eik aadmi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen merey haath par ya apney haath par shumar kya, farmaya : '' Subhanallah kehna nisf meezaan hai, aur Alhamdulillah kehna usey bhar deta hai, aur Allahu-akbar zamin w aasman ke darmiyan ko bhar deta hai, roza nisf sabr hai jabkey tahaarat nisf eman hai.'' Tirmizi aur Imam Tirmizi ne is hadees ko Hasan kaha hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3519 ( w ibne-Hibban (4 / 117 ( ."
297,"Hazrat Abdullah Sunabihi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab momin banda wuzu karta hai aur kulli karta hai to khataeyn uskey munh se nikal jati hain, jab naak jhadta hai to khataeyn uski naak se nikal jati hain, jab apna chehra dhota hai to khataeyn uskey chehrey se nikal jati hain, yahan tak ke uski aakhon ki palkon ke nichey se bhi nikal jati hain, chunanche jab wo apney haath dhota hai to khataeyn uskey haathon se nikal jati hain, yahan tak ke uskey haathon ke naakhunon ke nichey se nikal jati hain, chunanche jab wo apney sar ka masah karta hai to khataeyn uskey sar se yahan tak ke uskey kanon se nikal jati hain, jab wo apney paaon dhota hai to khataeyn uskey paaon yahan tak ke paaon ke naakhunon ke nichey se nikal jati hain, phir uska masjid ki taraf chalna aur uski Namaz uskey liye zayed ho jati hai.'' rawahu Malik (1 / 31, 59) w Nasai (1 / 74 , 75, 103 ( ."
298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabristaan tashrif laye to farmaya : '' un gharon ke rehney waley mominon tum par salamti ho, agar Allah ne chaha to ham bhi yaqinan tumharey paas pahunchney waley hain, meri khahish thi ke ham apney bhaiyon ko dekhtey.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! kya ham aap ke bhai nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum merey sathi ho, aur hamarey bhai wo hain jo abhi nahin aaye.'' Sahaba ne phir arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap apni ummat ke un afrad ko kaisey pahchaanengey jo abhi nahin aaye aur wo baad mein aaeyngey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao, agar kisi shakhs ka safed taangon aur safed peshani wala ghodaa, siyah ghodon mein ho to kya wo apney ghodey ko nahin pehchanega?'' Sahaba ne arz kya : kyon nahin Allah ke Rasool ! zarur pehchan lega , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pas wo aaeyngey to wuzu ki wajeh se unke haath paaon aur peshani chamakti hogi jabkey main hoze-kausar par unka pesh ro hunga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
299,"Hazrat abu-Darda bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat sab se pehley mujhey sajda karney ki ijazat di jaeygi aur sab se pehley mujhey sajde se sar uthaney ki ijazat di jaeygi, pas main apney samney dekhunga to tamam ummaton mein se apni ummat pehchan lunga, aur isi tarah apney peechey, isi tarah apney daain aur isi tarah apney baain taraf .'' to kisi shakhs ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap tamam ummaton mein se apni ummat ko kaisey pahchaanengey jabkey Nuh (Alaihissalam) se lekar aap ki ummat tak kitni ummaten hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wuzu ke nishaanaat ki wajeh se unke haath paaon aur peshani chamakti hogi , unke ilawa koi aur aisa nahin hoga aur main unhen isliye bhi pehchan lunga ke unhen unka nama aamaal daain haath mein diya jaeyga aur main unhen pehchan eik aur alamat se bhi lunga ke unki aulad unke aagey daud rahi hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 199,  22080 ( ."
300,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ka wuzu toot jaey to jab tak wo wuzu na karey uski Namaz qubul nahin hoti.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 135 w Muslim ."
301,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wuzu ke baghair Namaz qubul ki jati hai na maal haram se sadqa .'' rawahu Muslim."
302,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : mujhey kasrat se mazi aati thi, lekin main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kartey huey sharam mehsus karta tha kyonkey aap merey sasur they, pas maine Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha to unhoney aap se daryaft kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo sharm-gah dhoey aur wuzu karey.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 269 w Muslim ."
303,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' aag par paki hui chiz khaney par wuzu karo.'' الشیخ الامام الاجل محی السنہ (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : mazkura baala hadees ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ki wajeh se mansookh hai. ( rawahu Muslim w fi masaabeh( 205 ( ."
304,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bakri ke shaaney ka gosht khaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur) naya ( wuzu na kya. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 207 w Muslim ."
305,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha : kya ham bakri ka gosht kha kar wuzu keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum chaho wuzu karo aur agar chaho to na karo.'' usney phir puchha : kya ham oont ka gosht kha kar wuzu keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan, oont ka gosht kha kar wuzu kar.'' us shakhs ne puchha : kya bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz padh lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' usney puchha : oonton ke baadey mein Namaz padhun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
306,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs apney pet mein kuch gad-bad mehsus karey aur is par maamla mushtaba ho jaey ke aaya us se koi chiz nikli hai ya nahin to wo masjid se na nikley yahan tak ke wo koi aawaz sun ley ya badboo mehsus kar ley.'' rawahu Muslim ."
307,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne doodh piya to kulli ki aur farmaya : '' is mein chiknaahat hoti hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 211 w Muslim."
308,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke roz eik wuzu se ( mutaaddid ( namazein padhein aur mozon par masah kya, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, aapney is tarah pehley to kabhi nahin kya tha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' umr ! maine jaan-boojhkar aisey kya hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
309,"Hazrat Suwed bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwa khaibar ke moqe par wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huye, yahan tak ke khaibar ke zerrin ilaqey sahbaa par pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Asr ada ki, phir aapney zaade-raah talab kya to sirf sattu aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiye gaey aap ke farman ke mutabiq unhen bhigo diya gaya to phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aur ham ne usey khaya, phir aap namaze-Maghrib ke liye khadey huey to kulli ki aur ham ne bhi kulli ki, phir aapney Namaz padhi aur) naya ( wuzu na farmaya. Bukhari 209 ( ."
310,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aawaz ya badboo ( mehsus honey ( ki surat mein wuzu wajib hota hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 41, 9301) w Tirmizi ( 74 ( w ibne-Maja ( 515 ( ."
311,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine mazi ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mazi se wuzu aur mani se ghusl wajib hota hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi (114) w ibne-Maja ( 504 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 210 ( w Bukhari 132 , 269 w Muslim."
312,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tahaarat Namaz ki chaabi, takbir ( Allahu-akbar ( uski tehreem (us takbir se Namaz shuru karney se pehley jo kaam mabaah they wo haram ho jatey hain) aur taslim (Assalaamualaikum warahmatullah) uski tahleel hai : '' (yani salam pherney se Namaz ki surat mein haram honey waley kaam halal ho jatey hain) rawahu Abu-Dawood) w Tirmizi (3) w Darmi (1 / 175 padhi. 693 ( w ibne-Maja ( 275 ( w al-Behaqi ( 2 / 16 ( ."
313,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ( 276 ( .
314,"Hazrat Ali bin Talaq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein koi aawaz ke baghair hua khaarij karey to wo wuzu karey, aur tum aurton se unki peeth mein mujaamiat na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 1164 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 205 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 203 ( ."
315,"Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aankhen dubur (peeth) ka tasma hain, jab aankhen so jati hain to tasma khul jata hai.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 184 padhi. 728 ( ."
316,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''peeth ka tasma dono aankhen hain, pas jo shakhs so jaey to wo wuzu karey.'' al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : sahih hadees ki roshni mein ye hukm let kar soney waley shakhs ke liye hai, (bethey-bethey so janey waley ke liye nahin hai) rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 203 ( w ibne-Maja ( 477 ( ."
317,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) Namaz Isha ka intizar kartey rehtey yahan tak ke (neend ki wajeh sey) unke sar jhuk jatey, phir wo Namaz padhtey lekin wo (naya) wuzu na kartey. albatta Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat mein intizar ke badley so janey ka zikr kya hai, ke wo Isha ke waqt bethey so jatey yahan tak ke unke sar jhuk jatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood (200) w Tirmizi 78 w Muslim ."
318,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak jo shakhs chit let kar so jaey, is par wuzu karna lazim hai, kyonkey jab wo chit let jata hai to uskey jod dheeley ho jatey hain : ''rawahu Tirmizi (77) w Abu-Dawud ( 202 ( ."
319,"Hazrat Busra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apni sharm-gah ko haath lagaey to wo wuzu karey.'' rawahu Malik (1 / 42, 88) w Ahmed (6 / 406, 407 padhi. 27836, 27838 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 181 ( w Tirmizi (82) w Nasai (1 / 100 padhi. 163) w ibne-Maja ( 479 ( w Darmi (1 / 184 padhi. 730 ( ."
320,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aadmi ke wuzu kar leney ke baad apni sharm-gah ko haath laganey ke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha gaya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo ( sharm-gah ( bhi uskey gosht ka eik tukda hai.'' Sheikh imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye mansookh hai, kyonkey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Talaq (Raziallahu anhu) ki aamad ke baad musalman huey . rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 182 ( w Tirmizi (85) w Nasai (1 / 101, 165 ( w ibne-Maja ( 483 ( ."
321,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs apna haath apni sharm-gah ko lagaey jabkey us ( haath (aur us ( sharm-gah (ke darmiyan koi chiz haael na ho to wo wuzu karey.'' rawahu Shafai (1 / 19 ( w Dar-Qutni (1 / 147 padhi. 525 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 1115 ( al-Mustadrak (1 / 138 tehat padhi. 479 ( w Nasai (1 / 100 padhi. 163 ( ."
322,"Hazrat Imam Nasai ne usey Busra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, albatta unhoney ye zikr nahin kya, , uskey aur uskey beech koi chiz haael na ho.'' ."
323,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni kisi zauja mohtarma ka bosa ley liya kartey they, phir aap Namaz padhtey aur wuzu nahin kartey they. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Urwa an Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , aur Ibrahim Taimi (an) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki sanad se ye hadees hamarey as-haab ke yahan sahih nahin, aur Abu-Dawood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees mursal hai, aur Ibrahim Taimi ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se nahin suna ."
324,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dasti ka gosht khaya , phir apney nichey bichhi hui chadar se apna haath saaf kya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhi ."
325,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine bhuni hui pasli (chaanp) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is mein se tanaawul farmaya, phir Namaz ke liye uthey aur wuzu nahin kya. rawahu Ahmed."
326,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main gawahi deta hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye bakri ki kaleji aur dil waghera bhoona karta tha, (aapney usey khaya) phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahin kya.'' rawahu Muslim ."
327,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, unhen eik bakri hadiye ke taur par di gaee, to unhoney usey handiya mein dal diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laey to farmaya : ''abu-Raafe! ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! eik bakri hamen bator hadiya di gaee thi to maine usey handiya mein pakaaya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Raafe ! mujhey dasti do .'' maine dasti aap ko de-di, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey dusri dasti do.'' maine dusri dasti bhi aap ko de-di, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey aur dasti do.'' unhoney arz kya Allah ke Rasool ! bakri ki sirf do dastiyaan hoti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''agar tum khamosh rehtey aur jab tak khamosh rehtey to mujhey ek key baad dusri dasti milti rehti.'' phir aapney pani mangwaya, kulli ki aur apni ungliyon ke kinarey dhoey, phir khadey huey to Namaz padhi, phir dobara unke paas tashrif laye to unke yahan thanda gosht paya to usey khaya, phir aap masjid mein tashrif ley gaey to Namaz padhi, aur pani ko haath tak na lagaya."
328,"Darmi ne abu-Ubaid se riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney : '' phir pani mangaaya.'' se aakhir tak zikr nahin kya."
329,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main, Ubai bin Kab aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bethey huey they, pas ham ne gosht roti khai, phir maine wuzu ke liye pani mangaaya, to un dono ne kaha : tum wuzu kyon kartey ho? maine kaha is khaney ki wajeh se jo ham ne khaya hai, to unhoney kaha : kya tum pakizah chizon se wuzu kartey ho? ye chizen kha kar to us shakhsiyat (yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ne wuzu nahin kya jo tum se behtar hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
330,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : aadmi ka apni ehliya ka bosa lena aur usey apney haath se chhuna mulaamisa ke khaney mein hai, aur jo shakhs apni ehliya ka bosa ley ya usey apney haath se chhuey to is par wuzu karna lazim hai. rawahu Malik w Shafai."
331,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : apni ehliya ka bosa leney se wuzu karna zaroori hai. rawahu malik.
332,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : be-shak bosa lena, lams ke khaney mein aata hai, pas us ( wajeh ( se wuzu karo ."
333,"Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her qism ke behtey khoon ki wajeh se wuzu karna zaroori hai.'' dono hadeeson ko Daar-Qutni ne riwayat kya, aur unhoney kaha : umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) ne Tameem Daari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna na unhen dekha, jabkey Yazid bin Khalid aur Yazid bin Muhammad dono majhool hain."
334,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum qazaey-hajat ke liye jaao to qible ki taraf munh karo na pusht, balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf munh karo.'' muttafaq aleh. al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees sehra ke barey mein hai, raha imarat waghera mein qazaey-hajat karna to is mein koi harj nahin, jaisa ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai."
335,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apni kisi zarurat ke tehat ummul-momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar ki chhat par chadha to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qibley ki taraf pusht aur Sham ki taraf munh karkey qazaey-hajat kartey huey dekha. muttafaq aleh."
336,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne peshab-pakhaney ke liye qible ki taraf munh karney ya daain haath se istinja karney ya teen se kam dhelon se istinja karney ya leed ya haddi ke sath istinja karney se hamen mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
337,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) mein dakhil hotey to farmatey : ''aey Allah! main napak jinnon aur napak mada jinnat se teri panah chahta hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
338,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do qabron ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : '' un dono ko azab diya ja raha hai, aur unhen kisi badey gunah ki wajeh se azab nahin diya ja raha, un mein se eik peshab kartey waqt parda nahin kya karta tha, aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : peshab kartey waqt ehtiyat nahin kya karta tha, jabkey doosra shakhs chughal khor tha.'' phir aapney eik taza shaakh lekar uskey do tukdey kar diye, phir her qabr par eik tukda gaad diya, Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aapney ye kyon kya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mumkin hai unke khushk honey tak unke azab mein kami kar di jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
339,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lanat ka baais banney wali do chizon se bacho.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! lanat ka sabab banney wali do chizen kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo logon ki raah guzar ya unke saye ki jagah mein peshab-pakhana karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
340,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs koi chiz piye to wo bartan mein saans na ley, aur jab baitul-khala (toilet) mein jaey to apney daain haath se apni sharm-gah ko na chhuey aur daain se istinja bhi na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
341,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu karey to wo naak jhaadey aur jo dhelon se istinja karey to wo dheley taaq adad mein ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
342,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) mein jatey to main aur eik doosra ladka pani ka bartan aur barchhi uthatey, aur aap pani se istinja kartey.'' muttafaq aleh."
343,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khala (toilet) mein janey ka irada farmatey to aap apni anguthi utaar detey . usey Abu-Dawud, Nasai aur Tirmizi ne riwayat kya hai. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, aur Abu-Dawood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye riwayat munkar hai, unki riwayat mein (nazaa) ke bajaey (wazaa) ka lafz hai."
344,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab-pakhane ka irada farmatey to aap ( sehra ki taraf) chaltey jatey yahan tak ke aap nazron se ojhal ho jatey."
345,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, aapney peshab karney ka irada kya to aap deewar ki buniyad ke paas naram jagah aaye aur peshab kya. phir farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi peshab karney ka irada karey to wo peshab karney ke liye munasib jagah talash karey.''"
346,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat ka irada farmatey to aap (bethtey waqt) zamin ke qarib ho kar apna kapda uthaya kartey they."
347,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumharey liye isi tarah hun jis tarah walid apney bachey ke liye hota hai, main tumhen sikha sakta hun, jab tum peshab-pakhaney ke liye jaao to qible ki taraf munh karo na pusht, aapney (istinje ke liye) teen pathar istimal karney ka hukm farmaya, aapney leed aur haddi se (istinja karney sey) mana farmaya aur daain haath se istinja karney se mana farmaya.'' rawahu ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
348,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka daayan haath wuzu , aur khaney ke liye tha, jabkey baayan haath istinja aur naa-pasandida kamon ke liye tha.''"
349,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi peshab-pakhaney ke liye jaey to wo istinja karney ke liye apney sath teen dheley ley jaey, ye uskey liye kafi hongey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi."
350,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gobar aur haddi ke sath istinja na karo, kyonkey wo tumharey jin bhaiyon ki khurak hai.'' Tirmizi, Nasai . albatta Imam Nasai ne '' tumhari jin bhaiyon ki khurak '' ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w Muslim ."
351,"Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''Ruwefe! shayad merey baad tumhari umr daraz ho jaey, logon ko bata dena ke jisney apni dadhi ko gireh di ya galey mein taant dali ya janwer ki leed ya haddi se istinja kya to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se buri hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
352,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs surma lagaey to wo taaq adad mein lagaey , jisney aisey kya usney achcha kya, aur jisney aisey na kya to koi harj nahin, jo shakhs dheley se istinja karey to wo bhi taaq adad mein dheley istimal karey, jisney aisey kya to usney achcha kya aur jisney na kya to koi harj nahin, jo shakhs koi chiz khaye to jo tukdey khilal karney se niklen unhen phenk dey aur jo apni zaban ke zariey nikaley to unhen nigal jaey, jisney aisa kya usney achcha kya, aur jisney na kya to koi harj nahin, aur jo shakhs peshab-pakhaney ke liye jaey to wo parda karey, agar wo koi chiz na paey to wo ret ka eik teela sa banaey aur uski taraf pusht kar ley kyonkey shetan , aulad Adam ki maqad (peeth) ke sath khelta hai, jisney aisey kya usney achcha kya aur jisney na kya to koi harj nahin .''"
353,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi apney ghusl khaney mein peshab na karey, phir wo is mein ghusl karey ya wuzu karey, kyonkey ziyada tar waswasey isi (peshab) se hotey hain.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai . albatta un dono ne '' phir is mein ghusl karey ya wuzu karey.'' ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye."
354,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi bil (keedey makodon ki jagah) mein peshab na karey.''"
355,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen baaton se bacho , jinkey karney waley par lanat ki jati hai, pani ke ghaat, raastey ke darmiyan aur saye mein peshab-pakhana karney se.''"
356,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do shakhs peshab-pakhana kartey waqt uriyan haalat mein baham (aapas mein) baaten na karen, kyonkey Allah aisa karney par naraz hota hai.''"
357,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un maqamat par jinnat ka aana-jaana laga rehta hai lihaza jab tum mein se koi baitul-khala (toilet) jaey to ye dua padhey : ''main nar aur mada napak jinnat se Allah ki panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
358,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab un mein se koi baitul-khala (toilet) mein jaey to wo (bismillah) kahey. ye jinnon ki aakhon aur aulade-Adam ki parde ki chizon ( sharm-gah waghera) ke darmiyan parda aur aad hai.'' Tirmizi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur uski asnaad qawi nahin."
359,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se bahar tashrif latey to ye dua : ( غفرانک ( ''main teri maghfirat chahta hun.'' padha kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
360,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) jatey to main mitti ke bartan ya chamdey ki chhaagal mein aap ko pani pesh karta, aap istinja kartey, phir apna haath zamin par phertey, phir main eik doosra bartan peshe-khidmat karta to aap wuzu farmatey.'' Abu-Dawud, Darmi aur Nasai ne bhi unhi ke maana mein riwayat kya hai."
361,"Hazrat Hakam bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab kartey to wuzu farmatey aur apni sharm-gah par pani ke chheentey maartay they.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
362,"Hazrat Umaima bint Ruqeqa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki chaarpai ke nichey lakdi ka eik piyala hota tha jis mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt peshab kya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
363,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dekha, jabkey main khada peshab kar raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar! khadey ho kar peshab na karo.'' pas uskey baad maine kabhi khadey ho kar peshab nahin kya. al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees Sabit hai."
364,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi qom ke kudey-karkat ke dher par aaye to aapney khadey ho kar peshab kya. Imam Bukhari aur Imam Muslim ne riwayat kya hai aur kaha gaya hai ke ye ( khadey ho kar peshab karna ( kisi uzr ki wajeh se tha. muttafaq aleh.
365,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : jo shakhs tumhen ye bataey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar peshab kya kartey they, to uski tasdeeq na karo, aap to sirf beth kar peshab kya kartey they. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai ."
366,"Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke ''jab Jibrael pehli martaba unke paas wahi lekar aaye to unhoney aap ko wuzu aur Namaz sikhai, jab wuzu se farigh huey to chullu mein pani liya aur usey apni sharm-gah par chhidak diya .''"
367,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael merey paas aaye to unhoney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aap wuzu karen to (uskey baad sharm-gah par) pani chhidak liya keren.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur maine Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Hasan bin Ali Hashmi raawi munkire-hadees hai."
368,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne peshab kya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) pani ka lota liye aap ke peechey khadey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' umr ! ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : pani hai, aap is se wuzu farmaeyngey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ye hukm nahin diya gaya ke jab main peshab karun to wuzu bhi karun. agar main aisa karun to ye sunnat bin jaeygi.''"
369,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub, Jabir aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab ye aayat : ''us mein aisey log hain jo is baat ko pasand kartey hain ke paak saaf rahen, aur Allah paak saaf rehney walon ko pasand karta hai : ''nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ansaar ki jamaat ! Allah ne pakizgi ke barey mein tumhari tareef ki hai, tumhari pakizgi kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : ham her Namaz ke liye wuzu kartey hain, ghusle-janabat kartey hain aur pani se istinja kartey hain, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pas yehi wajeh hai, chunanche tum uski pabandi karo.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
370,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi mushrik ne mazaq mein kaha : mera khayal hai tumhara sathi (Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen peshab-pakhaney ke aadaab bhi sikhata hai, maine kaha : haan bilkul theek hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yehi hukm diya hai ke ham peshab-pakhaney ke waqt qibley ki taraf munh karen na daain haath se istinja karen aur ham ( istinje ke liye ( teen dhelon se kam istimal na karen, aur un mein leed aur haddi na ho.'' isey Muslim aur Ahmed ne riwayat kya hai mazkura alfaz Ahmed ke hain. rawahu Muslim w Ahmed ."
371,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye, aap ke haath mein chamdey ki dhaal thi, aapney usey rakha , phir beth kar uski taraf rukh karkey peshab kya, to un mein se kisi ne kaha : unhen dekho , kaisey aurat ki tarah ( chup kar) peshab kar rahey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski baat sun li , aur farmaya : ''tum par afsos hai, kya tum us se ba-khabar nahin jo Bani-Israel ke eik sathi ke sath hua ke jab unhen peshab lag jata to wo us hissey ko qainchi se kaat diya kartey they. chunanche us shakhs ne unko mana kar diya jiski wajeh se usey uski qabr mein azab diya gaya .''"
372,Hazrat Imam Nasai ne ye riwayat un ( Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu)) ki sanad se Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai.
373,"Hazrat Marwan Asfar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney apni sawari ko qibla rukh bithaya . phir uskey rukh beth kar peshab kya, maine arz kya : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya us se mana nahin kya gaya? unhoney farmaya : ( nahin) balke sirf khuli fiza mein us se mana kya gaya hai. agar tumharey aur qibla ke beech koi aisi chiz ho jo tumharey liye parda ho to phir ( qibla rukh peshab karney mein) koi harj nahin.''"
374,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se bahar tashrif laye to ye dua padhtey : '' her qism ki tareef w shukr Allah ke liye hai jisney mujh se takleef door ki aur mujhey aafiyat ata farmaey.''"
375,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Jinnon ka wafad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! apni ummat ko haddi ya leed ya koiley se istinja karney se mana farmaeyn, kyonkey Allah ne un chizon mein hamarey liye rizq rakha hai, pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen us se mana farma diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
376,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka andesha na hota to main unhen Namaze-Isha der se padhney aur her Namaz ke sath miswak karney ka hukm farmata.'' muttafaq aleh."
377,"Hazrat Shureh bin Haani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se daryaft kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar tashrif latey to aap sab se pehley kon sa kaam kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : miswak . rawahu Muslim ."
378,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat tahajjud ke liye uthtey to aap miswak se apney munh ko saaf kartey. muttafaq aleh."
379,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' das khaslatein fitrat se hain : moochhein kutarna, dadhi badhaana, miswak karna, naak mein pani chadhana , nakhun kutarna, ungliyon ke jod dhona , baghlon ke baal ukhedna , zere-naf baal mundna aur istinja karna , raawi bayan kartey hain, daswin khaslat main bhool gaya hun, mumkin hai wo kulli karna ho. eik riwayat mein dadhi badhaney ke bajaey khatnon ka zikr hai. maine ye riwayat na saheehain mein paai hai na kitabul-Humaidi mein, lekin sahib '' الجامع '' aur isi tarah al-khattabi ne '' muaalimus-sunan'' mein isey zikr kya hai. rawahu Muslim ."
380,Hazrat Abu-Dawood ne Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat se zikr kya hai.
381,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''miswak munh ko saaf karney wali aur rab ki razamandi ka baais hai.'' Shafai, Ahmed, Darmi, Nasai aur Imam Bukhari ne isey apni sahih mein muallaq bayan kya hai."
382,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar chizen tamam Rasulon ki sunnat hain : haya, kisi riwayat mein khatney ka zikr hai, atr lagana, miswak karna aur nikah karna.''"
383,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ya din ke kisi hissey mein sotey to aap bedaar ho kar wuzu karney se pehley miswak kya kartey they."
384,"Hazrat Aaisha bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) miswak kya kartey they, phir aap miswak mujhey dey detey taake main usey dho dun to main dhoney se pehley khud miswak karti, phir usey dho kar aap ko lota deti.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
385,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine apney aap ko khuwab mein miswak kartey huey dekha chunanche us doran do aadmi merey paas aaye, un mein se eik doosrey se bada tha, maine un mein se chhotey ko miswak de-di, to mujhey kaha gaya : badey ko do, chunanche maine badey ko de-di.'' muttafaq aleh."
386,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael jab bhi merey paas tashrif latey to aap mujhey miswak karney ka hukm farmatey, mujhey to andesha hua ke main kahin apney munh ka samney ka hissa na chheel dun .''"
387,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen miswak ke barey mein bahut martaba kaha hai.'' Bukhari ."
388,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) miswak kar rahey they aur aap ke paas do aadmi they, un mein se eik doosrey se bada tha, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chhodi hui miswak ke barey mein aap ki taraf wahi aai ke ye badey ko dey den .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
389,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' miswak karkey padhi gaee Namaz , miswak ke baghair padhi gaee Namaz se sattar guna afzal hai.''"
390,"Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu), Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka andesha na hota to main unhen her Namaz ke waqt miswak karney ka hukm deta aur Namaz Isha ko tihai raat tak muakhkhar karta.'' Zaid bin Khalid masjid mein namazein padhney ke liye aatey to kaatib ke qalam ki tarah unki miswak unke kaan par hoti thi, aur wo jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to miswak kartey aur phir usey uski jagah (kaan) par rakh detey. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, albatta unhoney ''main Namaze-Isha ko tihai raat tak muakhkhar karta"" ke alfaz zikr nahin kiye. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
391,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi neend se bedaar ho to wo apna haath bartan mein na daley yahan tak ke usey teen martaba dho ley, kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uskey haath ne raat kahan basar ki.'' muttafaq aleh."
392,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs neend se bedaar ho kar wuzu karey to wo teen martaba naak jhaadey, kyonkey shetan uski naak mein raat basar karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
393,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaisey wuzu kya kartey they? pas unhoney wuzu ke liye pani mangaaya, to apney haathon par pani dala aur do do martaba haath dhoey, phir teen martaba kulli ki aur naak jhaadi, phir teen martaba apna chehra dhoya, phir dono haathon ko kohniyon samet do do martaba dhoya, phir apney haathon se sar ka masah kya aur unhen sar ki agli taraf se guddi tak ley gaey aur phir sar ki agli taraf jahan se shuru kya tha wapis ley aaye, phir apney dono paaon dhoey. malik, Nasai, aur Abu-Dawood mein isi tarah hai, sahib '' الجامع '' ne bhi usey zikr kya hai. muttafaq aleh."
394,"aur saheehain mein hai ke Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu karkey dikhayen, pas unhoney pani ka eik bartan mangaaya, aur is mein se kuch pani apney haathon par undela, aur unhen teen martaba dhoya, phir apney haath ko pani ke bartan mein dala aur is mein pani lekar eik hi chalo se kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala, unhoney ye teen martaba kya, phir unhoney apna haath bartan mein dal kar us se pani nikala aur teen martaba apna chehra dhoya, phir apna haath bartan mein dala aur pani nikal kar do do martaba haathon ko kohniyon samet dhoya, phir apna haath bartan mein dal kar us se aur pani nikal kar apney sar ka masah kya, apney haathon ko aagey ley gaey aur wapis laye, phir unhoney takhnon tak paaon dhoey , phir unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu usi ki misl tha. eik riwayat mein hai sar ka masah kartey waqt haathon ko sar ki agli janib se guddi tak ley gaey aur phir unhen wahin wapis ley aaye jahan se shuru kya tha, phir apney dono paaon dhoey . eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aapney teen martaba kulli ki, naak mein pani dala aur naak jhaadi aur aisa teen chalo pani ke sath kya. eik aur riwayat mein hai : aapney eik chullu ke sath hi kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala aur aapney aisa teen martaba kya. Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : aapney sar ka masah kya, aap haathon ko aagey ley gaey aur wapis laye. aapney ye eik martaba kya, phir aapney takhnon tak dono paaon dhoey, aur Bukhari ki dusri riwayat mein hai : aapney eik hi chullu se teen martaba kulli ki aur naak jhaadi. muttafaq aleh."
395,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik eik martaba wuzu ke angon ko dhoya, aur us se ziyada nahin kya. Bukhari."
396,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do-do martaba wuzu ke angon ko dhoya. Bukhari .
397,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney maqaaid ( Madina ke paas jagah ( par wuzu kya, to farmaya : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa wuzu na dikhaaun? chunanche unhoney wuzu kartey waqt teen-teen baar wuzu ke angon ko dhoya. rawahu Muslim ."
398,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Makka se Madina wapis aa rahey they, yahan tak ke ham raastey mein pani ke paas se guzrey, kuch logon ne namaze-Asr ke liye jaldi ki, pas unhoney ujlat mein wuzu kya, chunanche jab ham unke paas pahunchey to dekha ke unki eidiyaan (khushk honey ki wajeh sey) chamak rahi thin, un tak pani nahin pahuncha tha, pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ediyon ke liye jahannam ki aag hai, wuzu khub achi tarah mukammal karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
399,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to aapney apni peshani, amaama aur mozon par masah kya. rawahu Muslim ."
400,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney tamam umur (baton) ( maslan ( wuzu karney , kanghi karney aur joota pehanney mein daain taraf se shuru karna maqdoor bhar pasand kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
401,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum libas pahno aur jab tum wuzu karo to apni daain taraf se shuru karo.''"
402,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu kartey waqt bismillah na padhey uska wuzu nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
403,Hazrat Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
404,"aur Darmi ne abu-Saeed Khudri an Abeeh ki sanad se riwayat kya hai, aur uskey shuru mein izafa kya hai : ''jiska wuzu nahin uski Namaz nahin.''"
405,"Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey wuzu ke mutalliq bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wuzu achi tarah karo, ungliyon ke darmiyan khilal karo aur roza ki haalat ke ilawa naak mein pani khub chadhaao .'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , aur ibne-Maja aur Darmi ne ( bainul-asaabee ( tak riwayat kya hai."
406,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum wuzu karo to apney haathon aur apney paaon ki ungliyon ka khilal karo.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai, aur Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
407,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wuzu farmatey to apni chhoti ungli ke sath paaon ki ungliyon ko khub maltey. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
408,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wuzu farmatey to chullu mein pani lekar thodi ke nichey dakhil kartey aur us se apni dadhi ka khilal kartey, aur farmatey : ''merey rab ne mujhey isi tarah hukm farmaya hai.''"
409,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni dadhi ka khilal kya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi .
410,"Hazrat Abu-Haiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kya to apney haath dhoey aur unhen khub achi tarah saaf kya, phir teen martaba kulli ki, teen baar naak saaf ki, teen baar chehra dhoya , teen baar bazu dhoey , eik martaba sar ka masah kya, phir takhnon tak paaon dhoey , phir khadey huey aur wuzu se bacha hua pani khadey ho kar piya , phir farmaya : maine chaha ke tumhen dikhaaun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu kaisey tha. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
411,"Hazrat Abd Khair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kya to ham bethey unhen dekh rahey they, chunanche unhoney apna daayan haath bartan mein dala (aur us se pani lekar (apney munh aur naak mein dala phir baaeyn haath se naak saaf ki, aapney teen martaba aisey hi kya, phir farmaya : jisey pasand ho ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu dekhey to ye aapka wuzu hai. rawahu Darmi ."
412,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney eik hi chullu se kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala, aur aapney teen martaba aisey hi kya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
413,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney sar ka masah kya, aur aapney kanon ke andar ke hisson ka shahadat ki ungliyon se aur bahar ke hisson ka anguthon se masah kya. rawahu Nasai ."
414,"Hazrat Rabeea binte-Muawwiz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu kartey huey dekha, unhoney kaha : aapney-apney sar ki agli janib aur pichli janib (purey sar) ka, dono kanpatiyon aur dono kanon ka eik martaba masah kya, aur eik riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to apni do ungliyan apney dono kanon ke suraakhon mein dalin. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi ne pehli riwayat bayan ki jabkey Ahmed aur ibne-Maja ne dusri ."
415,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney wuzu kya aur ye ke aapney apney haathon ke sath lagey huey pani ke ilawa alag pani se sar ka masah kya. Tirmizi jabkey Muslim ne kuch zawaayed ke sath riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 35 w Muslim (19 / 236 ( .
416,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wuzu ka zikr kartey huey farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dono gosha chashm ( dono aakhon ke naak se milney waley hissey (ka masah kya kartey they, neez aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ke '' kaan sar ka hissey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ( 444 ( w abu-Dawud ( 134 ( Tirmizi (37). aur dono (Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Tirmizi ( ne zikr kya ke Hammad ne kaha : mujhey malum nahin ke '' kaan sar ka hissa hain.'' ye abu-Umama ka qol hai ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hai."
417,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney baap se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik dehati Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney aap se wuzu ke mutalliq puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen-teen martaba wuzu ke angon dho kar usey dikhaye , phir farmaya : ''is tarah ( mukammal ( wuzu hai, pas jisney is se ziyada martaba kya usney bura kya, had se tajawuz kya aur zulm kya. '' Nasai , ibne-Maja jabkey Abu-Dawood ne usi maana mein riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai w ibne-Maja w abu-Dawud w ibn Khuzaima ."
418,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apney bete ko dua kartey huey suna : ''aey Allah ! main tujh se jannat ke daain taraf safed mehal ki darkhast karta hun, to unhoney farmaya : beta ! Allah se jannat ki darkhast karo aur jahannam se uski panah talab karo, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' an-qareeb meri ummat mein kuch aisey log hongey jo wuzu (ke aazaa dhoney) aur dua karney mein had se tajawuz karengey .'' rawahu Ahmed w abu-Dawud w ibne-Maja."
419,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dorane-wuzu waswasa dalney waley shetan ka naam ''Walhaan'' hai, chunanche pani ke istimal ke waqt waswason se bacho.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, iski sanad muhaddeseen ke nazdik qawi nahin, kyonkey ham nahin jantey ke khaarija ( raawi (ke ilawa kisi aur ne usey marfoo riwayat kya hai, jabkey wo hamarey as-haab ke nazdik qawi nahin."
420,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney wuzu kya to apney kapdey ke kinarey se apney chehrey ko saaf kya."
421,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kapdey ka eik tukda tha, aap uskey sath wuzu ke baad apney aazaa saaf kya kartey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees sahih nahin, abu-Muaaz raawi , muhaddeseen ke nazdik zaeef hai."
422,"Hazrat Sabit bin Abu-Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine abu-Jaafar Muhammad Baaqar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ko ye hadees bayan ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik-eik martaba, do do martaba aur teen teen martaba wuzu kya hai? unhoney kaha : haan ."
423,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do do martaba wuzu kya aur farmaya : '' wo Noor par noor ( soney pe suhaaga ( hai.'' Rizeen ( )
424,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen teen martaba wuzu kya aur farmaya : ''ye mera , mujh se pehley Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ka wuzu hai. Rizeen ne dono riwaayatein kin , jabkey Imam Nauwii ne Sharah sahih Muslim mein dusri riwayat ko zaeef . qarar diya hai."
425,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her Namaz ke liye wuzu kya kartey they, jabkey hamarey kisi ke liye (pehla) wuzu kafi rehta hai jab tak uska wuzu na tootey. rawahu Darmi w Bukhari."
426,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Yahya bin Hibban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin umr se kaha : tum ne Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko her Namaz ke liye wuzu kartey huey dekha hai? qata-nazar iskey ke wo pehley hi ba-wuzu they ya be wuzu neez unhoney ye masla kahan se liya hai? unhoney kaha : Asma bint Zaid bin Khattab ne unhen hadees bayan ki ke Abdullah bin Hanzala bin abi Aamir al-Ghaseel ne unhen hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu honey ya wuzu na honey her do Suraton mein her Namaz ke liye wuzu karney ka hukm diya gaya, chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ye giraan guzra to aap ko her Namaz ke waqt miswak karney ka hukm diya gaya aur wuzu ka hukm khatm kar diya gaya albatta wuzu na honey ki surat mein wuzu karney ka hukm baqi raha , raawi bayan kartey hain, Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) samajhtey they ke unhen her Namaz ke liye naya wuzu karney ki istataat hasil hai lihaza wo martey dam tak is par amal paira rahey . rawahu Ahmed ."
427,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey jabkey wo wuzu kar rahey they, aapney farmaya : ''Saad! ye kaisa israaf hai?'' unhoney arz kya : kya wuzu karney mein bhi israaf hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, chahey tum nehar rawan par hun.''"
428,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), ibne-Masood aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne wuzu kya aur Bismillah padhi usney apna pura jism paak kar liya, aur jo shakhs wuzu karey lekin Bismillah na padhey to wo sirf wuzu ke angon hi paak karta hai.''"
429,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye wuzu kartey to aap apni anguthi ko ungli mein hilaatey they. dono riwaayaton ko Dar-Qutni ne riwayat kya hai, aur ibne-Maja ne aakhiri ko riwayat kya hai."
430,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi us (yani apni ehliya ( ki chaar shaakhon ke darmiyan bethey, phir usey mashaqqat mein mubtala (yani jimaa) karey to ghusl wajib ho jata hai, chaahey inzaal na ho'' muttafaq aleh."
431,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pani ( ghusl (pani) mani ke nikalney) se hai.'' rawahu Muslim. al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees mansookh hai."
432,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : pani pani se hai, ye ehtilaam ke barey mein hai. Tirmizi, aur maine usey saheehain mein nahin paya ."
433,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! be-shak Allah haq baat se nahin sharmata, jab aurat ko ehtilaam ho jaey to kya is par ghusl karna wajib hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, jab wo pani (mani ke aasaar) dekhay.'' ( ye sun kar) Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne apna chehra dhanp liya aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aurat ko bhi ehtilaam hota hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , tera daayan haath khaak aalud ho, to phir uska bachcha us se kaisey mushaabihat ikhtiyar karta?'' muttafaq aleh."
434,"Hazrat Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke tareeq se jo riwayat bayan ki hai is mein ye izafa naqal kya hai : ''aadmi ka pani gaadha safed hota hai, jabkey aurat ka pani patla zard hota hai, pas un dono mein se jiska pani ghalib aa jaey ya sabqat ley jaey to bachey ki mushaabihat usi par ho jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
435,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat farmatey to aap sab se pehley haath dhotey , phir wuzu farmatey jaisey Namaz ke liye wuzu kya jata hai, phir apni ungliyan pani mein dakhil kartey aur us se apney baalon ki jadon ka khilal kartey , phir apney sar par teen lap pani daltey , phir apney purey jism par pani bahaatey . muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl farmatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney haathon ko kisi bartan mein dalney se pehley dhotey , phir apney daain haath se baaeyn haath par pani daltey aur apni sharm-gah ko dhotey, phir wuzu farmatey."
436,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan (Raziallahu anhu) kartey hain, Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye ghusl karney ke liye pani rakha , aur eik kapdey se aap par parda kya, aapney apney dono haathon par pani dala to unhen dhoya , phir aapney apney haathon par pani dala to unhen dhoya , phir apney daain haath se baaeyn haath par pani dal kar sharm-gah ko dhoya, phir aapney apna haath zamin par mala aur usey dhoya, phir aapney kulli ki, naak mein pani dala, apna chehra aur bazu dhoey, phir sar par pani dala, aur sarey jism par pani bahaaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us jagah se hat kar paaon dhoey, maine aap ko kapda diya lekin aapney na liya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haathon se pani saaf kartey tashrif ley gaey. aur ye alfaz Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
437,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ansaar ki eik khatoon ne ghusl haiz ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bataya ke wo kaisey ghusl karegi, phir farmaya : ''kastoori laga hua rui ka eik tukda lekar is se tahaarat hasil karo.'' usney arz kya : main is se kaisey tahaarat hasil karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is se tahaarat hasil karo.'' usney phir arz kya : main is se kaisey tahaarat hasil karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subhan Allah! is se tahaarat hasil karo.'' ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ( pas maine usey apni taraf khinch liya aur bataya : usey khoon ki jagah ( sharm-gah ( par rakh ley . muttafaq aleh."
438,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main eik aisi aurat hun ke main apney sar ke baalon ko mazbut goondhti hun, to kya main ghusle-janabat ke liye usey khol diya karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, tumharey liye yehi kafi hai ke tum apney sar par teen lap pani dalo , phir apney jism par pani baha lo , pas tum paak ho jaaogi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
439,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik mud (taqreeban chhe so gram / mili litre ( se wuzu aur eik saa (chaar mud) se paanch mud tak pani se ghusl kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
440,"Hazrat Muaza bayan karti hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan sey, jo ke hamarey darmiyan hota tha, ghusl kya kartey they, aap mujh se jaldi farmatey they yahan tak ke main kehti : merey liye (pani) rehney den , merey liye rehney den , jabkey wo dono junbi hotey they. muttafaq aleh."
441,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us aadmi ke mutalliq masla puchha gaya jo (apney jism ya kapdon par) nami paata hai lekin usey ehtilaam yad nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo ghusl kerega .'' aur phir us shakhs ke mutalliq masla puchha gaya jo samajhta hai ke usey ehtilaam hua hai lekin wo koi nami nahin paata , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is par ghusl lazim nahin.'' umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : kya aap aurat par bhi ye ghusl wajib samajhtey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , kyonkey aurten bhi) takhleeq w tabiat mein) mardon ki tarah hain.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi aur ibne-Maja ne ( la ghusl aleh ( tak riwayat kya hai."
442,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab mard ki sharm-gah aurat ki sharm-gah mein dakhil ho jaey to ghusl wajib ho jata hai, main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey kya to ham ne ghusl kya. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
443,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her baal ke nichey janabat hai, baal dhoo aur jism ko saaf karo.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, Haris bin Wajeeh raawi umr raseeda hai, aur uski riwayat ki tosiq nahin ki ja sakti ."
444,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne baal barabar jaey janabat chhod di aur usey na dhoya to usey jahannam mein is is tarah ki saza di jaeygi .'' Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine isi liye apna sar munda liya, maine isi liye apna sar munda liya, maine isi liye apna sar munda liya ye jumla aapney teen martaba farmaya. Abu-Dawud, Ahmed, Darmi.۔ albatta un dono ( Ahmed aur Darmi ( ne maine usi liye apna sar mundaa liya '' ka takraar zikr nahin kya."
445,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl ke baad wuzu nahin kya kartey they.
446,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khitmi se apna sar dhoya kartey they jabkey aap junbi hotey they, aap usi par iktifa farmatey aur is par pani nahin daltey they."
447,"Hazrat Yala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi shakhs ko khuley maidan mein) nangey) ghusl kartey huey dekha, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif laye aur Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''beshak Allah hayadar, parda poshi karney wala hai, wo hayadari aur parda poshi ko pasand farmata hai, pas jab tum mein se koi nahaaey to wo parda karey.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai . aur Nasai ki eik riwayat mein hai : ''be shak Allah parda poshi karney wala hai, pas jab tum mein se koi ghusl karna chahey to wo kisi chiz se parda kar ley.''"
448,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, pani ( ghusl ), pani ( inzaal ( ki wajeh se wajib hota hai, is barey mein shuru Islam mein rukhsat thi, phir us se mana kar diya gaya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
449,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, maine ghusle-janabat kya aur maine namaze-Fajr ada ki, phir maine nakhun barabar jagah khushk dekhi jahan pani nahin pahuncha tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum apna geela haath is par pher detey to wo tumharey liye kafi hota.''"
450,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain namazein pachas thin, ghusle-janabat saat martaba tha, kapdey se peshab dhona bhi saat martaba tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) musalsal (kami ke liye apney rab sey) sawal kartey rahey yahan tak ke namazein paanch, ghusle-janabat eik martaba aur peshab ki wajeh se kapdey ka dhona eik martaba kar diya gaya."
451,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mujh se mulaqat hui mein us waqt junbi tha, pas aapney mujhey haath se pakda to maine aap ke sath chalna shuru kya yahan tak ke aap beth gaey to main wahan se chupkey se utha aur ghar aa kar ghusl karkey phir khidmat mein hazir hua to aap wahin tashrif farma they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abu-Hurera ! tum kahan they?'' maine arz kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Subhanallah ! momin najas nahin hota.'' ye Bukhari ke alfaz hain. aur Muslim ki riwayat bhi uskey ham-maani hai. aur unhoney ''maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya '' ke baad nichey likhi ka izafa naqal kya hai : ''jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley to main junbi tha, pas maine ghusl kiye baghair aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ham-nasheen hona napasand kya.'' Bukhari ki dusri riwayat bhi isi tarah hai. muttafaq aleh."
452,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya ke wo raat ko junbi ho jatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' wuzu kar, istinja kar aur so ja.'' muttafaq aleh."
453,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) junbi hotey aur aap khaney ya soney ka irada farmatey to aap Namaz ke wuzu jaisa wuzu farmatey. muttafaq aleh."
454,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apni ehliya se jima karey aur phir wo dobara jima karna chahey to wo un dono ke darmiyan wuzu kar ley.'' rawahu Muslim ."
455,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni azwaaje-mutahraat (paak biviyon) ke paas ghusle-wahid ke sath chakkar laga liya kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
456,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her haalat mein Allah azz-w-jall ka zikr kya kartey they. rawahu Muslim . aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ham inshaAllah Taala , kitab al-atama mein zikr karengey"
457,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja mohtarma ne eik tab mein ghusl kya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se ghusl karna chaha to unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main to junbi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pani junbi nahin hota .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , jabkey Darmi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
458,"Hazrat Sharahus-sunnah mein Memuna an-ibne-Abbas, masaabeh ke alfaz se marwi (bayan) hai."
459,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat kya kartey phir aap mujh se garmaaish hasil kartey jabkey maine abhi ghusl nahin kya hota tha. ibne-Maja , Tirmizi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai. Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke alfaz hain."
460,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se bahar tashrif latey to hamen Quran padhatey aur hamarey sath gosht tanaawul farmatey aur janabat ke ilawa koi aur chiz aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Quran se maane (rukawat) nahin thi. Abu-Dawud, Nasai , jabkey ibne-Maja ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
461,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haaiza aur junbi shakhs Quran se kuch na padhein.''"
462,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un gharon ke darwazey masjid ke dusri taraf kar lo, kyonkey main haaiza aur junbi ke liye masjid ko halal qarar nahin deta.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
463,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ghar mein tasweer , kutta aur junbi hun wahan ( rehmat w barkat ke) farishtey nahin jatey. '' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
464,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke log hain ke) rehmat w barkat ke) farishtey unke qarib bhi nahin jatey, kafir ki laash, Khalooq (Zaafran ki khushbu) se lithdey huey shakhs aur junbi siwaey iske ke wo wuzu kar ley.''"
465,Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Bakr bin Muhammad bin Amr bin hazam se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Amr bin hazam ke naam jo khat likha is mein tehreer tha : '' sirf paak shakhs hi Quran ko haath laga sakta hai.'' rawahu Malik w Dar-Qutni.
466,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, main kisi kaam ki gharz se ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath gaya, pas jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kaam mukammal kar liya to unhoney us din eik hadees sunai ke eik aadmi kisi gali se guzra to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mila jabkey aap peshab-pakhaney se farigh ho kar aa rahey they, us shakhs ne aap ko salam kya, lekin aapney usey jawab na diya, yahan tak ke qarib tha ke wo aadmi gali mein se ojhal ho jata . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney dono haath deewar par maarey aur unhen apney chehrey par mala, phir dobara haath maarey to unhen baazuon par mal liya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aadmi ke salam ka jawab diya, aur farmaya : ''tumharey salam ka jawab deney mein sirf yehi eik rukawat thi ke main us waqt baa-wuzu nahin tha.''"
467,"Hazrat Muhajir Qanfaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jabkey aap peshab kar rahey they, pas unhoney aap ko salam kya lekin aapney wuzu kar leney tak salam ka jawab na diya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mazrat ki aur farmaya : ''maine wuzu ke baghair Allah ka zikr karna na pasand kya. '' Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ne (حتی توضا) tak riwayat kya, aur farmaya : jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya to uskey salam ka jawab diya."
468,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) junbi ho jatey , phir so jatey , phir bedaar hotey aur phir so jatey."
469,"Hazrat Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ghusle-janabat kartey to wo saat martaba daain haath se baaein hath par pani daltey, phir sharm-gah dhotey, pas wo ye bhool gaey ke unhoney kitni martaba pani dala , unhoney mujh se puchha to maine kaha : main nahin janta , unhoney kaha : teri maa na rahey, tumhen kis ne roka ke tum na jano , phir wo Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu kartey , phir apney jism par pani bahaatey , phir farmatey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah ghusl kya kartey they."
470,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik roz apni azwaj (jodey) mutahraat ke paas gaey, aur her eik ke paas jatey waqt ghusl farmaya , wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kyon na aap sab se aakhir par eik hi ghusl farma letey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ziyada pakizah , ziyada achcha aur ziyada saaf hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
471,"Hazrat Hakam bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mard ko aurat ke ghusl se bachey huey pani se wuzu karney se mana farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Tirmizi . Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , Tirmizi aur unhoney kuch izafa naqal kya, ya farmaya : ''uskey joothe se.'' aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
472,"Hazrat Humaid al-Himyari bayan kartey hain, main eik aadmi se mila jisey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se chaar saala sohbat ka sharf hasil tha, usney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurat ko mard ke ghusl se bachey huey pani se aur mard ko aurat ke ghusl se bachey huey pani se ghusl karney se mana farmaya .'' Musaddad ne izafa naqal kya : '' chahiye ke dono ikhattey chullu bharen.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai . aur Imam Ahmed ne uskey shuru mein ye izafa naqal kya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her roz kanghi karney ya ghusl khaney mein peshab karney se hamen mana farmaya."
473,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey Abdullah bin Sarjis se riwayat kya hai.
474,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs khadey pani mein jo ke behta na ho, peshab na karey, phir wo is mein ghusl karey.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai. ''tum mein se koi shakhs khadey pani mein ghusle-janabat na karey.'' logon ne puchha : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ! wo kaisey karey ? farmaya : wo wahan se pani ley aur) dusri jagah par ghusl karey ( ."
475,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey pani mein peshab karney se mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
476,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri khaala mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley gaeen aur unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mera bhaanja mareez hai, chunanche aapney merey sar par haath phera aur barkat ke liye dua ki, phir aapney wuzu kya, to maine aap ke wuzu ka pani piya , phir main aap ke peechey khada ho gaya to maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kandhon ke beech chakor ke anday ki misl mohre-nabuwat dekhi. muttafaq aleh."
477,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us pani ke mutalliq puchha gaya jo jangal mein ho aur wahan chopaaey aur darindey pani peeney ke liye aatey jatey hon, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab pani do matkey (taqreeban saadhey chhe man) ho to wo gandagi qubul nahin karta.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai, Darmi, ibne-Maja. aur Abu-Dawood ki dusri riwayat mein hai : '' wo najas nahin hota.''"
478,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha gaya : kya ham Bizaa ke kunwen se wuzu kar liya karen jabkey wo aisa kunwaan hai, jahan haiz aalud kapdey , kutton ke gosht aur badboo daar chizen phenki jati hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak pani paak hai, usey koi chiz napak nahin karti .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
479,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kya, ham samandari safar kartey hain aur thoda sa pani apney sath ley jatey hain, agar ham us se wuzu kartey hain to phir piyasey reh jatey hain, to kya ham samandar ke pani se wuzu kar liya keren? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uska pani paak hai aur uska murdar halal hai.'' rawahu Malik w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
480,"Hazrat Abu-Zaid, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke jis raat jin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' tumhari chhaagal mein kya hai? '' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : nabeez hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khajoor umda chiz hai pani paak hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Imam Ahmed, aur Imam Tirmizi ne ye izafa naqal kya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se wuzu farmaya. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : Abu-Zaid maj-hool hai."
481,"aur Alqama se sahih sanad se Sabit hai ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jis raat jin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey they, main us raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nahin tha. rawahu Muslim ."
482,"Hazrat abu-Qatada ke bete ki ehliya Kabsha bint Kab bin Malik se riwayat hai, ke abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas tashrif laye to usney unke wuzu ke liye bartan mein pani dala , itney main eik billi aa kar us se peeney lagi to unhoney uskey liye bartan jhuka diya yahan tak ke usney pi liya, Kabsha bayan karti hain, unhoney mujhey dekha ke main unki taraf dekh rahi hun, to unhoney farmaya : bhatiji ! kya tum tajjub karti ho? wo bayan karti hain, maine kaha : ji haan , unhoney kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye najas nahin, kyonkey wo tumharey paas kasrat se aaney waley khaadimon aur kasrat se aaney wali laundiyon ke khaney mein hai.'' rawahu Malik w Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
483,"Hazrat Dawud bin Saleh bin Dinar (Raziallahu anhu) apni walida se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apni azad karda londi ke haath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke liye harisa (Halim ki tarah ka khana ( bheja , wo bayan karti hain, maine unhen Namaz padhtey huey paya to unhoney usey rakh deney ka mujhey ishara farmaya, eik billi aai aur usney is mein se kha liya, jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Namaz se farigh huin to unhoney usi jagah se khaya jahan se billi ne khaya tha, aur unhoney kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo najas nahin, kyonkey wo tumharey paas kasrat se aaney waley khaadimon mein se hai.'' aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uskey bachey huey pani se wuzu kartey huey dekha hai."
484,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha gaya : kya ham gadhey ke bachey huey pani se wuzu kar lein ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , darindon ke bachey huey ( joothe (pani se bhi .''"
485,"Hazrat Umme- Hani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ne bartan mein ghusl kya jis mein aatey ka nishan tha."
486,"Hazrat Yahya bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) kuch sawaron ke sath , jin mein Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they rawana huey yahan tak ke wo eik hoz par pahunchey, to Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaaya: hoz ke malik! kya terey hoz par darindey bhi pani peeney aatey hain? umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : hoz ke malik! hamen na batana, kyonkey darindon ke baad ham peeney aa jatey hain, aur hamarey baad wo aa jatey hain."
487,"Rizeen ne kaha : baaz raawiyon ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke qol mein ye izafa naqal kya hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo un (darindon) ke pet mein chala gaya, wo unka, aur jo bach raha wo hamarey liye paak hai aur baaise-tahaarat aur peeney ke laaiq hai.'' ( لااصل لہ ( rawahu Rizeen ."
488,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan waqey un taalaabon se tahaarat hasil karney mein masla puchha gaya jahan se darindey, kuttey aur gadhey pani peetey hain, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhoney jo pi liya wo unka aur jo bach gaya wo hamarey liye paak hai.''"
489,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : dhoop se garm kiye gaey pani se ghusl na karo kyonkey wo baras (phal bahari) ka marz paida karta hai.
490,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kutta tumharey kisi shakhs ke bartan mein se pi ley to usey saat martaba dhoo.'' Bukhari, Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''jab kutta tumharey kisi shakhs ke bartan mein munh dal dey to us bartan ki pakizgi is tarah hasil hogi ke usey saat martaba dhoya jaey, un mein se pehli martaba mitti se saaf kya jaey.''"
491,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik dehati khada hua to usney masjid mein peshab kar diya, log usey daantney lagey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kuch na kaho, aur uskey peshab par eik dol pani baha do, kyonkey tumhen to aasani ke liye bheja gaya, tangi paida karney ke liye nahin.'' Bukhari ."
492,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath masjid mein bethey huey they ke is beech main eik dehati aaya aur wo khada ho kar masjid mein peshab karney laga, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne kaha : ruk ja , ruk ja , jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska peshab na roko , usey kuch na kaho chhod do .'' chunanche unhoney usey chhod diya yahan tak ke usney peshab kar liya , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bula kar farmaya : ''ye jo masaajid hain ye peshab aur gandagi waghera ke liye munasib nahin, ye to Allah ke zikr, Namaz aur qirat Quran ke liye hain.'' ya phir jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un logon mein se kisi shakhs ko hukm farmaya to wo pani ka dol ley aaya to aapney wo us (peshab) par baha diya. muttafaq aleh."
493,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, eik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kartey huey arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke agar ham mein se kisi ke kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag jaey to wo kya karey ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag jaey to wo usey naakhunon se khurch ley phir usey pani ke sath dhoey aur phir us (kapdey) mein Namaz padhey .'' muttafaq aleh."
494,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine kapdey ko lag janey wali mani ke barey mein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : main usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey se dho diya karti thi, pas aap Namaz ke liye tashrif ley jatey , jabkey dhoney ka nishan aap ke kapdey mein hota . muttafaq aleh."
495,"Hazrat Aswad aur Hammam (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey se mani ragad diya karti thi. rawahu Muslim ."
496,"Hazrat Alqama bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se isi tarah marwi (bayan) hai, neez us riwayat mein ye bhi hai : phir aap us ( kapdey ( mein Namaz padhtey. rawahu Muslim ."
497,"Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo apney chhotey sher khuwar bete ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey apni god mein bitha liya, usney aap ke kapdey par peshab kar diya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pani mangaa kar is par chhidak diya aur usey dhoya nahin. muttafaq aleh."
498,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab chamdey ko rang diya jata hai to wo paak ho jata hai. rawahu Muslim."
499,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ki azad karda londi ko sadqe ke taur par eik bakri di gaee, pas wo mar gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''tum ne uski khaal kyon na utaar li, pas tum usey rang detey aur us se faeyda uthatey.'' unhoney arz kya, ye to murdar hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf uska khana haram qarar diya gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
500,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Sauda (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, hamari bakri mar gaee to ham ne uski khaal ko rang liya , phir ham is mein nabeez tayyar kartey rahey yahan tak ke wo boseedah ho gaee. Bukhari."
501,"Hazrat Lubaba binte-Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki god mein they, unhoney aap ke kapdey par peshab kar diya, maine arz kya, aap doosra kapda pehan lein, aur apna izaar mujhey dey den taake main usey dho dun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf ladki ke peshab se kapda dhoya jata hai, aur ladkey ke peshab se kapdey par chheentey maarey jatey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
502,"Hazrat Abu-Dawood aur Nasai mein abul-Masah (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bachchi ke peshab se kapda dhoya jata hai jabkey ladkey ke peshab se kapdey par chheentey maarey jatey hain.'' ."
503,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ke jootey ko gandagi lag jaey to mitti usey paak kar deti hai.'' Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja mein bhi usi ke ham-maani hai."
504,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne unhen kaha : main apney kapdey ka daman lamba rakhti hun, jabkey main napak jagah se guzarti hun, unhoney bataya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo us (napaak jagah) ke baad hai wo usey paak kar degi.'' Malik , Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi. Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Darmi ne bataya ke wo aurat Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ki umme-walad thin ."
505,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darindon ki khaal pehanney aur un par sawari karney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
506,"Hazrat abul-Maleeh bin Usama apney walid se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darindon ki khalon (ke istimal) se mana farmaya hai. Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Nasai. Imam Tirmizi aur Darmi ne izafa naqal kya hai : ye ke unka bistar banaya jaey."
507,"Hazrat abul-Maleeh se riwayat hai ke aapney darindon ki khalon ki qeemat (yani bai) ko napasand farmaya hai. us riwayat ko Imam Tirmizi ne'' aapney darindon ke chamdey ko napasand farmaya hai, ke alfaz ke sath zikr kya hai aur iski sanad jaiyed hai."
508,Hazrat Abdullah bin Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khat Mausool hua ke ''murdar ke chamdey se faeyda uthao na uskey aasaab (putthon) se.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja .
509,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm farmaya ke ''jab murdar ka chamdaa ranga jaey tab us se faeyda hasil kya jaey.'' rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood .
510,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain Quraish ke kuch afrad apni ( murdar ( bakri ko gadhey ki misl ghaseet'tey huey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzrey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''tum uska chamda hi utaar letey.'' unhoney arz kya : ye murdar hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pani aur (keekar ke mushabeh darkht aur uskey pattey) usey paak kar detey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood .
511,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ghazwa tabuk ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik gharaney ke paas tashrif laye to wahan eik mishkeeza latak raha tha, aapney pani talab kya, to unhoney aap se arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye to murdar hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey rang dena hi uski tahaarat hai.''"
512,"Hazrat Abdul-Ashhal ki eik khatoon bayan karti hain maine arz kya Allah ke Rasool! masjid ki taraf hamara jo raasta hai wo intehai ganda aur badbudar hai jab barish ho jaey to phir ham kya keren? wo bayan karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya uskey baad us se koi ziyada behtar aur pakizah raasta nahin?'' maine arz kya ji haan hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski gandagi us se door ho jati hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
513,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they aur ham gandagi par chal kar janey ki wajeh se wuzu nahin kya kartey they."
514,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah ke zamaney mein kuttey masjid mein aatey jatey rehtey they aur wo (Sahaba kiraam) uski kisi chiz ko dhoya nahin kartey they. Bukhari .
515,Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis janwer ka gosht khaya jata ho uskey peshab mein koi muzaaeqa nahin.''
516,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ka gosht khaya jaey uskey peshab mein koi muzaaeqa nahin .''"
517,Hazrat Shureh bin Hani bayan kartey hain maine Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se mozon par masah karney ( ki muddat (ke barey mein masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musafir ke liye teen din aur muqeem ke liye eik din muddat muqarrar farmaai hai. rawahu Muslim .
518,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwa tabuk mein shirkat ki, Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr se pehley peshab-pakhaney ke liye khuli jagah tashrif ley gaey, main pani ka bartan utha kar aap ke sath gaya, pas jab aap wapis tashrif laye to maine bartan se aap ke haathon par pani dala, to aapney apney haath aur chehra dhoya, aapney ooni jubba pehan rakha tha, aapney bazu nangey karney ki koshish ki, lekin jubbe ki aasteen tang thin, lihaza aapney jubbe ke nichey se haath nikaley aur jubbey ko apney kandhon par dal liya aur apney bazu dhoey, phir aapney peshani aur amaama par masah kya, main aapkey mozey utaarney ke liye jhuka to aapney farmaya : ''unhen chhod do, kyonkey maine unhen haalate-wuzu mein pehna tha.'' aapney un par masah kya, phir aap sawari par Sawar huey aur main bhi Sawar hua jab ham lashkar ke paas pahunchey to wo Namaz khadi kar chukey they aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) unhen Namaz padha rahey they, aur wo unhen eik rakat padha chukey they, chunanche jab unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aamad ka ehsas hua to wo peechey hatney lagey, aapney unhen ishara kya ke Namaz padhtey raho, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik rakat unke sath pa li, jab unhon ( Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) ne salam phera to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey . aur main bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khada ho gaya, to ham ne wo rakat padhi jo ham se pehley padhi ja chuki thi. rawahu Muslim."
519,"Hazrat abu-Bakra Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musafir ko teen din aur muqeem ko eik din mozon par masah karney ki rukhsat inayat farmaai b-sharte-ke unhoney wuzu ke baad mozey pehney hon.'' Asram ne apni sunan mein, ibne-Khuzaima aur Dar-Qutni ne usey riwayat kya hai, Khattabi ne kaha : wo sahih al-asnaad hai."
520,Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jab ham musafir hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen hukm farmatey ke ham janabat ke ilawa peshab-pakhaney aur neend ki surat mein teen din tak apney mozey na utaaren . rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai.
521,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain maine ghazwa tabuk ke moqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu karaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mozon ke ooper aur nichey masah kya. Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Malool hai maine abu-Zaraa aur Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari se is hadees ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye hadees sahih nahin aur isi tarah Abu-Dawood ne bhi isey zaeef qarar diya hai."
522,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon ke ooper masah kartey huey dekha . rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood.
523,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu farmaya aur aapney juraabon aur jooton par masah kya."
524,"Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mozon par masah kya to maine arz kya Allah ke Rasool! kya aap bhool gaey hain? aapney farmaya : ( nahin), balke tum bhooley ho merey rab azz-w-jall ne mujhey isi ka hukm farmaya.''"
525,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, agar Deen ka daromadar aql w raey par hota to mozon par nichey masah karna unke ooper masah karney se afzal w behtar hota jabkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon ke ooper masah kartey huey dekha hai. Abu-Dawood ; aur Darmi ne bhi isi maana mein riwayat kya hai."
526,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamen baqi ummaton par teen chizon se fazilat di gaee hai, hamari safon ko farishton ki safon jaisa qarar diya gaya, hamarey liye sari zamin masjid qarar di gaee aur uski mitti ko, jab ham pani na paeyn, tahaarat ka zaria banaya gaya.'' rawahu Muslim ."
527,"Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rafeeqe-safar they, aapney logon ko Namaz padhaai, pas jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko alag betha hua dekha jisney ba-jamaat Namaz nahin padhi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''falan shakhs! tumhen ba-jamaat Namaz ada karney se kis cheez ne roka tha? '' usney arz kya, main junbi ho gaya tha aur maine pani nahin paya , aapney farmaya : ''tum mitti istimal kartey , wo tumharey liye kafi thi .'' muttafaq aleh."
528,"Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur usney arz kya : main junbi ho gaya hun, lekin mujhey pani nahin mila , ( ye sun kar) Ammar ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya aap ko yad nahin, ke ham eik martaba safar mein they, aapney Namaz na padhi , jabkey main mitti mein lot pot hua , aur Namaz padh li , phir maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey liye is tarah karna kafi tha.'' chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath zamin par maarey aur un mein phunk maari, phir un se apney chehrey aur haathon par masah kya. Bukhari, muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim mein bhi isi tarah hai, aur is mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey liye kafi tha ke tum apney haath zamin par maartay, phir is mein phunk maartay aur phir unke sath apney chehrey aur haathon par masah kartey.''"
529,"Hazrat abu-Jaheem bin Haris bin Simma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra, jabkey aap peshab kar rahey they, maine aap ko salam kya to aapney mujhey jawab na diya, yahan tak ke aap eik deewar ki taraf gaey aur apni lathi se usey kureda, phir apney haath deewar par rakhey, aur apney chehrey aur bazuon ka masah kya, phir mujhey salam ka jawab diya. ye riwayat mujhey saheehain mein mili na kitabul-Humaidi mein, lekin unhoney Sharahus-sunnah mein usey zikr kya hai aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai."
530,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' paak mitti, musalman ke liye wuzu ke pani ki tarah hai chahey wo das saal tak pani na paey, lekin jab pani mil jaey tab us se apni jild tar karey kyonkey ye behtar hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Imam Nasai ne (Ashr sineen) tak isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
531,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik safar par rawana huey to ham mein se eik aadmi ko pathar laga jisney uska sar zakhmi kar diya, aur usi doran usey ehtilaam ho gaya, usney apney sathiyon se daryaft kartey huey kaha, kya tum merey liye tayammum ki rukhsat paatey ho? unhoney kaha : ham tumharey liye koi rukhsat nahin paatey kyonkey tumhen pani muyassar hai. pas usney ghusl kya jis se uski maut waqey ho gaee, jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to aap ko us barey mein bataya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' unhoney usey maar dala, Allah unhen halak karey, jab unhen masla malum nahin tha to unhoney puchha kyon nahi, la-ilmi ka ilaj poochh lena hai, uskey liye yehi kafi tha ke wo tayammum karta, zakhm par patti baandh leta, phir is par masah kar leta aur baqi sarey jism ko dho leta .'' Abu-Dawood ."
532,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Ata bin abi Ribah ki sanad se ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
533,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, do aadmi safar par rawana huye, Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, jabkey unke paas pani nahin tha, chunanche unhoney paak mitti se tayammum kya aur Namaz padhi, phir unhoney Namaz ke waqt hi mein pani pa liya , to un mein se eik ne wuzu karkey Namaz lautaai, jabkey doosrey ne na lautaai, phir wo dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur us waqia ka tazkira kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us shakhs sey, jisney Namaz na lautaai, farmaya : ''tum ne sunnat par amal kya aur tumhari Namaz tumharey liye kafi hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne, jis shakhs ne wuzu karkey Namaz lautaai thi, usey farmaya : ''tumharey liye dohra ajr hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Darmi, aur Nasai ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai."
534,Hazrat Imam Nasai aur Abu-Dawood ne bhi Ata bin Yasar se mursal riwayat kya hai.
535,"Hazrat Abul-Jaheem bin Haris bin Simma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jamal kunwe ( kunwen ka naam) ki taraf se aaye to eik aadmi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mila, usney aap ko salam kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey jawab na diya yahan tak ke aap deewar ke paas tashrif laye, apney chehrey aur haathon ka masah kya, phir usey salam ka jawab diya. muttafaq aleh."
536,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein namaze-Fajr ke liye mitti se tayammum kya to unhoney apney haath mitti par maarey , phir eik martaba apney chehron par masah kya, phir unhoney dobara dusri martaba apney haath mitti par maarey to apney sarey haathon par kandhon aur baghlon samet mukammal taur par masah kya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
537,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi ( Namaz ( Juma ke liye aaye to wo ghusl karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
538,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Juma ke din ghusl karna her baligh shakhs par wajib hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
539,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hafte main eik roz ghusl karna her musalman par lazim hai, jis mein wo apna sar aur jism (achi tarah) dhoey.'' muttafaq aleh."
540,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Juma ke roz wuzu kya to usney achcha kya, aur jisney ghusl kya to ghusl karna afzal hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai w Darmi ."
541,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maiyat ko ghusl dey to wo khud bhi ghusl karey.'' ibne-Maja, Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : ''jo shakhs usey kandha dey to wo wuzu karey.'' ."
542,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar chizon : janabat , Jume ke din, seengi lagwaaney aur maiyat ko ghusl denay, se ghusl kya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
543,Hazrat Qais bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Islam qubul kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke wo pani mein beri ke pattey dal kar ghusl karen. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai .
544,"Hazrat Ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ehale-Iraq se kuch log aaye aur unhoney arz kya : ibne-Abbas! kya aap Juma ke roz ghusl karna wajib samajhtey hain? unhoney farmaya : nahin, lekin pakizgi ka baais aur behtar hai, aur jo shakhs ghusl na karey to is par wajib nahin, main tumhen batata hun ke ghusl ka aaghaz kaisey hua, log mehnat-kash they, ooni libas pehantey they, wo apni kamar par bojh uthatey they, unki masjid tang thi aur chhat oonchi nahin thi, bas wo eik chhappar sa tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) garmiyon ke din tashrif laye to log us ooni libas mein paseeney se sharabor they, yahan tak ke un se bu phel gaee aur wo eik doosrey ke liye baaise-aziyat bin gaee, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye bu mehsus ki to farmaya : ''logo! jab ye (Jume ka ( din ho to ghusl karo aur jo behtareen tel aur khushbu muyassar ho wo istimal karo.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : phir Allah ne maal ata kar diya to unhoney ghair-ooni kapdey pehan liye, kaam karney ki zarurat na rahi. unki masjid ki tausee kar di gaee aur eik doosrey ko aziyat pahunchaney wali wo paseeney ki bu jati rahi. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
545,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, yahudiyon ka ye tarze-amal tha ke jab un mein kisi aurat ko haiz aa jata to wo uskey sath khatey na unhen ghar mein sath rakhtey, pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne aap se masla puchha to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ''wo aap se haiz ke barey mein masla daryaft kartey hain.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jimaa ke ilawa sab kuch karo.'' chunanche yahudiyon ko uska ilm hua to unhoney kaha ye aadmi (nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) kya chahta hai ye tamam maamlat mein hamari mukhalifat hi karta hai. chunanche Usaid bin Huzair aur Ibada bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) hazire-khidmat huey to unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! Yahudi ye ye kehtey hain, kya ham un se ( haalate-haiz mein) jima na keren? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya, yahan tak ke un dono ne khayal kya ke aap un dono par naraz ho gaey hain, pas wo wahan se chal diye, unhen doodh ka hadiya mila jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja gaya tha, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi shakhs ko unke peechey bheja aur unhen doodh pilaya jis se unhoney pehchan liya ke aap un par naraz nahin. rawahu Muslim ."
546,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan se ghusl kya kartey they, jabkey ham dono junbi hotey they, aap mujhey hukm detey to main izaar pehan leti , phir aap merey sath let jatey jabkey main haiz se hoti, aap aetikaf ki haalat mein apna sar Mubarak meri taraf kar detey, to main usey dho deti halanke main haiz se hoti thi. muttafaq aleh."
547,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main haalate-haiz mein koi chiz peeti phir main usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dey deti to aap usi jagah apna munh lagatey, jahan maine munh lagaya tha. aur main haddi wali boti khati jabkey main haiz se hoti thi, phir main usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dey deti to aap usi jagah munh lagatey jahan mera munh laga tha. rawahu Muslim ."
548,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri god mein tek lagatey, aur Quran Hakim ki tilawat farmatey halanke main us waqt makhsus dinon mein hoti thi. muttafaq aleh."
549,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''mujhey masjid se chatai pakda do.'' maine arz kya, main haiz se hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak tera haiz terey haath mein nahin .'' rawahu Muslim ."
550,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ooni chadar mein Namaz padha kartey they, uska kuch hissey mujh par hota aur kuch aap par hota, jabkey main haiz se thi. muttafaq aleh."
551,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne haaiza se jima kya ya aurat se lawatat ki ya wo kisi kaahin ke paas gaya to usney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par nazil ki gaee shariyat ka inkar kar diya.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi. aur ibne-Maja aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai : ''agar usney us (kaahin ki) baat ko sacha jana to bila-shuba usney kufr kya.'' Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ham ye hadees sirf Hakimul-Asr an abi tameema an abi Huraira ki sanad se jantey hain."
552,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! jab meri ehliya haalate-haiz mein ho to uski kya chiz merey liye halal hai? aapney farmaya : ''jo chiz izaar se ooper hai, lekin us se bhi bachna afzal hai.'' Rizeen ne usey riwayat kya aur Muhiussunna ne farmaya : uski asnaad qawi nahin."
553,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apni ehliya se ayyame-haiz mein mujaamiat karey to wo nisf Dinar sadqa karey.''"
554,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jab ( haiz ka ( khoon surkh ho to (jimaa karney ki surat mein) eik Dinar aur jab khoon zard ho to nisf deenar.''"
555,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla poochhtey huey arz kya : jab meri ehliya haalate-haiz mein ho to uski kya chiz merey liye halal hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska izaar kas kar baandh , phir us se ooper ka hissa terey liye halal hai.'' Malik aur Darmi ne mursal riwayat kya hai."
556,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab mujhey haiz aata to main bistar se chatai par aa jati, aur jab tak ham paak na ho jatin ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib na jatin."
557,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Fatima binte-abi Habish Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaen aur unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main istihaze ki mareez hun, main paak nahin rehti , kya main Namaz chhod dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, wo to eik rag ka khoon hai, haiz nahin, pas jab tumhen haiz aaye to Namaz chhod do , aur jab wo jata rahey to khoon saaf kar (yani ghusl kar) aur phir Namaz padh .'' muttafaq aleh."
558,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) Fatima binte-abi Habish (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhen istihaza ka marz tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''jab haiz ka khoon hoga to wo siyah rang ka hoga aur wo aasani se pehchaana jata hai, jab wo ho to Namaz na padh aur jab doosra ( khoon (ho to phir wuzu kar aur Namaz padh , wo to mehaz rag ka khoon hai.''"
559,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik aurat ko istihaza ka khoon aata tha, Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne uskey barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aapney farmaya : ''usey chahiye ke us marz mein mubtala honey se pehley , usey mahiney mein jitney din haiz ka khoon aata tha, unhen shumar karkey itney din mahiney mein Namaz chhod dey , aur jab wo din guzar jaayein to wo ghusl karey aur kapdey ka langot baandh ley aur phir Namaz padhey.'' Malik , Abu-Dawud, Darmi , jabkey Nasai ne bhi usi maana mein riwayat kya hai."
560,"Hazrat Adi bin Sabit apney baap se aur wo us ( Adi (ke dada se riwayat kartey hain, Yahya bin Mueen ne kaha : Adi ke dada ka naam Dinar hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne istihaza mein mubtala aurat ke barey mein farmaya : '' wo apney ayyame-haiz ka lihaz rakhtey huey itney din Namaz na padhey, phir wo ghusl karey, aur her Namaz ke liye wuzu karey. aur wo roza rakhey aur Namaz padhey.''"
561,"Hazrat hamna binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, mujhey nihayat shadeed qism ka marz istihaza tha, mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai taake aap ko uskey mutalliq bataaun aur masla daryaft karun, chunanche maine unhen apni behan Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar paya to maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey shadeed qism ka istihaza laahiq hai, aap is barey mein mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? usney to mujhey Namaz rozey se rok rakha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen rui istimal karney ka mashwara deta hun, kyonkey wo khoon rok degi.'' unhoney arz kya : wo us se kahin ziyada hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to phir langot kas ley.'' unhoney arz kya : wo us se bhi kahin ziyada hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir langot ke nichey koi kapda rakh ley.'' unhoney arz kya, maamla us se kahin ziyada shadeed hai, main to pani ki tarah khoon bahaati hun, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen do baton ka hukm deta hun, tum ne un mein se jo bhi kar li, wo doosrey se kifaayat kar jaeygi, aur agar tum dono ki taqat rakho to phir tum ( apni haalat ke mutalliq ( behtar jaanti ho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''ye to eik shetani bimari hai, tum mamool ke mutabiq chhe ya saat din tak apney aap ko haaiza tasawwur kar liya karo, phir ghusl karo yahan tak ke jab tum samjho ke tum paak saaf ho gaee ho to 23 ya 24 din Namaz padho aur roza rakho, ye tumharey liye kafi hoga, aur tum her maah isi tarah kya karo jis tarah haiz wali aurten apney makhsus dinon mein aur us se paak honey ke baad karti hain, aur agar tum ye taqat rakho ke namaze-Zohar ko muakhkhar kar lo aur namaze-Asr ki jaldi kar lo , phir Zohar w Asr ko ikhatta padh lo, isi tarah maghrib ko muakhkhar kar lo aur Isha ko pehley kar lo, phir ghusl karkey dono namazein ikhatti padh lo, pas aisey kya karo, aur namaze-Fajr ke liye ghusl karo, aur roza rakho , agar tum aisa kar sako to karo.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aur dono umur (baton) mein se mujhey ye ( ghusl karkey Namaz jama karna ( ziyada pasandida hai.''"
562,"Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Fatima bint Habish (Raziallahu anhu) itni muddat se istihaze mein mubtala hai, aur usney us doran namaz nahin padhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subhan Allah! ye (istihaza) shetan ki taraf se hai, wo eik bartan mein bethey, agar wo pani ke ooper zardi dekhey to wo Zohar w Asr ke liye eik ghusl karey, maghrib w Isha ke liye eik ghusl karey aur Fajr ke liye eik ghusl karey aur unke beech (zohar w Asr ke ghusl ke beech) wuzu kar ley.''"
563,"aur usney kaha ke Mujahid ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, jab uskey liye ghusl karna mushkil ho gaya to aapney usey do namazein ikhatti padhney ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Darmi."
